### İterasyon 1 — Intake Backend (Report Create)

**Hedef:** Report oluşturma API'si; 18 kategori, dinamik alan encrypt, tracking code üretimi, KVKK consent kaydı.

**Yapılacaklar:**

1. `apps/api/src/modules/intake/` — module, controller, service
2. `POST /api/v1/intake/reports` — Zod DTO (`packages/dto`); `@AuditAction`; rate limit (10 req/dk/IP)
3. `GET /api/v1/intake/categories`, `GET /api/v1/intake/kvkk-text`, `GET /api/v1/intake/companies`
4. `tracking_code` üretimi — format `ETK-XXXX-XXXX` (12 karakter alfanümerik, unique)
5. `tracking_code_password_hash` — argon2id (memory ≥64 MB, iterations ≥3, parallelism ≥1)
6. Hassas alan encrypt: `incident_description`, `category_specific_data`, `reporter_identity_*`, `reporter_contact_*` via `CryptoService`
7. `kvkk_consent_version` zorunlu kayıt
8. Prisma migration: `reports` tablosu (`02` §Report)
9. Unit + integration test: report create roundtrip; encrypted alan DB'de ciphertext

**Minimum bağlam:**

