### İterasyon 3 — File Upload (Presigned + Quarantine + ClamAV)

**Hedef:** Async dosya yükleme pipeline; presigned URL pattern; quarantine → scan → AVAILABLE/REJECTED.

**Yapılacaklar:**

1. `POST /api/v1/intake/reports/:trackingCode/attachments` — presigned URL döner (client PUT)
2. `POST /api/v1/tracking/attachments` — tracking guard korumalı upload
3. MIME + uzantı whitelist; boyut limiti (`07` §5.2)
4. Quarantine state: upload sonrası PENDING_SCAN; worker async ClamAV scan
5. `apps/worker/src/jobs/clamav-scan.job.ts` — temiz → AVAILABLE, enfekte → REJECTED (quarantine'de kalır)
6. `ReportAttachment` Prisma model + migration
7. Integration test: presigned flow mock; infected file → REJECTED; sync scan yok

